Web Scraping Website/Software used
- Apify
  Extenstion of apify: Best Reddit Scrapper

Pre-Processing Software
- Excel 
  What we Store 
    -Author ID
    -Body(contain the Opinion)
    -URL(url of the Post)

Using Python Libraries NLTK :: Natural Language Toolkit to be used to analyze the opinion of respondent also known as text mining.

Libraries to be installed:
  pip
  pandas
  textblob
  openpyxl

Exported as csv. to be used in weka for further mining.


